Sentencas: Samaria-doped ceria (Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9, SDC) membranes for anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells were fabricated by a Slurry spin coating method.
Titulo: Preparation of Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9 membranes on porous substrates by a slurry spin coating method and its application in IT-SOFC

Sentencas: Comparative studies were carried out on the effect of the agglomerate property of SDC powders on the fabrication of the membranes.
Titulo: Preparation of Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9 membranes on porous substrates by a slurry spin coating method and its application in IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The results showed that the agglomerate property of the SDC powders had a significant effect on the formation of dense and thin SDC membranes.
Titulo: Preparation of Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9 membranes on porous substrates by a slurry spin coating method and its application in IT-SOFC

Sentencas: Using a Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (BSCF)-SDC composite cathode, the cell with a similar to 15 mu m SDC electrolyte membrane achieved all excellent performance.
Titulo: Preparation of Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9 membranes on porous substrates by a slurry spin coating method and its application in IT-SOFC

Sentencas: Maximum power densities of the cell were 648 and 869 mW cm(-2) at 600 and 650 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Preparation of Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9 membranes on porous substrates by a slurry spin coating method and its application in IT-SOFC

Sentencas: Analysis of the impedance spectra indicated that the cell resistance under open-circuit conditions was dominated by the interfacial resistance.
Titulo: Preparation of Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9 membranes on porous substrates by a slurry spin coating method and its application in IT-SOFC
